    <h2>file upload code</h2>
    <p>포인트: @RequestParam, MultipartFile, transferTo</p>
    <div class="content-box-inner">
        <div class="cbi-title"><p><span><a href="https://github.com/kangyongho/springboot-demo/blob/feature/file-upload/src/main/java/net/ddns/HelloController.java">
